@page "/cards-grid"
<PageTitle>Cards Grid - Saascade Docs</PageTitle>

<h1 id="cards-grid">Cards Grid</h1>

<div class="doc-layout">

<main class="documentation">

    <section class="card">

        <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>

        <p class="subtitle">
            The <code>&lt;CardsGrid&gt;</code> component renders a responsive
            grid container for <code>&lt;Card&gt;</code> components.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h3>Basic Usage</h3>

        <pre><code>&lt;CardsGrid&gt;
    &lt;Card&gt;
        &lt;CardBody&gt;
            &lt;CardTitle&gt;Card 1&lt;/CardTitle&gt;
            &lt;P&gt;First card content.&lt;/P&gt;
        &lt;/CardBody&gt;
    &lt;/Card&gt;
    &lt;Card&gt;
        &lt;CardBody&gt;
            &lt;CardTitle&gt;Card 2&lt;/CardTitle&gt;
            &lt;P&gt;Second card content.&lt;/P&gt;
        &lt;/CardBody&gt;
    &lt;/Card&gt;
&lt;/CardsGrid&gt;</code></pre>

    </section>

    <section class="card">

        <h2 id="related-components">Related Components</h2>

        <ul>
            <li><a href="cards">Card</a> — individual card container.</li>
            <li><code>&lt;CardBody&gt;</code> — card content wrapper.</li>
            <li><code>&lt;CardTitle&gt;</code> — card heading.</li>
        </ul>

    </section>

</main>

